---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Img_V from '@/assets/images/vertical.webp'
import Img_H from '@/assets/images/horizontal.avif'
---
<article>
  <div class="images-container">
    <Image 
      src={Img_V}
      alt={"Mobile screen"}
      class="mobile"
    />
    <Image 
      src={Img_H}
      alt={"Desktop screen"}
      class={'desktop'}
    />
  </div>
  <div class="info-container">
    <h3>MY ANIME APP</h3>
    <p>Una web para amantes de la cultura otaku, los usuarios podran mantener un control y registro personalizado de sus series favoritas, por medio de listas personalizadas donde cada serie podra tener puntuaciones y comentarios para que nunca olvides como te sentiste al verla por primera vez. </p>
    <div class="techs-container">
      <Icon name="tabler:brand-tailwind" width={30} height={30} />
      <Icon name="tabler:brand-react" width={30} height={30} />
      <Icon name="tabler:briefcase" width={30} height={30} />
      <Icon name="tabler:briefcase" width={30} height={30} />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="links-wrapper">
    <div class="links-container">
      <div>
        <Icon name="tabler:briefcase" width={30} height={30} />
      </div>
      <div>
        <Icon name="tabler:briefcase" width={30} height={30} />
      </div>
      <div>
        <Icon name="tabler:briefcase" width={30} height={30} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  article {
    --opacity: .2;
    --light_bg:hsla(0, 18%, 100%, var(--opacity));
    position: relative;
    gap: 12px;
    display: grid;
    width: 100%;
    border-block: 3px solid var(--pink-600);
    border-radius: 20px;
    background-color: var(--light_bg);
    overflow: hidden;

    .images-container {
      position: relative;

      .mobile {
        height: auto;
        width: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .desktop {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: contain;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
    }
    .info-container {
      display: grid;
      height: 100%;
      gap: 12px;
      place-items: center;

      h3 {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0px;
        left: 0;
        padding: 3vw;
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--light_bg), hsla(0, 18%, 100%, 0));
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        color: var(--pink-950);
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        padding-inline: 8px;
        text-wrap: pretty;
      }

      .techs-container {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-evenly;

        svg {
          height: 30px;
          width: 30px;
        }
      }
    }

    .links-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-evenly;
      background-color: var(--pink-600);
      padding: 7px;
      position: relative;
      
      &::after, &::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: -19px;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background-color: transparent;
      }
      &::before {
        right: 0;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 100%;
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 4px var(--pink-600);
      }
      &::after {
        left: 0;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 100%;
        box-shadow: -4px 4px 0px 4px var(--pink-600);
      }
      
      div {
        background-color: var(--pink-950);
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;

        svg {
          height: 32px;
          width: 32px;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media screen and (width >= 768px) {
    article {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      height: 400px;
      border: none;
      overflow: visible;
      border-right: 3px solid var(--pink-600);
      background: linear-gradient(to left, var(--light_bg), hsla(0, 18%, 100%, 0));
      
      &::after {
        content: " ";
        width: 60%;
        height: 100%;
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        right: 0;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;
        border-top-right-radius: 20px;
        border-bottom:2px solid var(--pink-600);
      }

      .images-container {
        grid-column: span 2;
        height: clamp(300px, 100%, 370px);
        width: 250px;

        .mobile {
          position: relative;
          top: -20px;
          height: 100%;
        }

        .desktop {
          position: absolute;
          right: clamp(-200px, -20vw, -150px);
          z-index: 20;
          bottom: -20%;
          width: 110%;
          height: auto;
          object-fit: contain;
          box-shadow: -2px 2px 4px 0px var(--pink-900);
        }
      }

      .info-container {
        grid-column: span 3;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        align-items: center;
        height: fit-content;

        h3 {
          position: relative;
          place-self: end;
          padding: 16px;
          background: none;
          backdrop-filter: none;
          text-align: end;
        }

        p {
          margin-right: 60px;
          width: 85%;
        }

        .techs-container {
          width: 30%;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          align-self: center;
          margin-top: 20px;
          display: flex;
          gap: 10px;
          justify-content: space-evenly;

          svg {
            height: 40px;
            width: 40px;
          }
        }
      }
      .links-wrapper {
        position: absolute;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        padding-top: 20px;
        padding-left: 20px;
        overflow: hidden;

        .links-container {
          display: grid;
          gap: 10px;
          padding-bottom: .8rem;
          padding-top: 25px;
          border-radius: 0;
          border-bottom-right-radius: 18px;
          border-top-left-radius: 100% 40px;
          
          &::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 1px;
            top: auto;
            left: -19px;
            border-radius: 0;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 100%;
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 4px var(--pink-600);
          }

          &::before {
            top: -17px;
          }
          
          div{
            svg{
              height: 24px;
              width: 24px;
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }  
  }
  
</style>